.PP
Get the system data directory path\&. The function first gets \fRXDG_DATA_HOME\fP variable, and returns if it is set\&. If not, it will try to get \fRHOME\fP variable and return the path as \fRHOME/\fP\&.local/share if avaliable\&. If failed, then it will return \fRNULL\fP in the path part\&. 
.PP
